---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="Web Designers Near Me vs Big Agencies: Why Shelby NC Businesses Are Choosing Local"
  description="Discover why Shelby, NC businesses are choosing local web designers over big agencies for better communication, value, and local SEO results."
>
  <article class="pt-32 pb-24 px-4 bg-[#0A0A0A]">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <!-- Header -->
      <header class="mb-16 text-center">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 mb-6 px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full border border-brand-cyan/20 bg-brand-cyan/5">
          <span class="text-brand-cyan text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">Vol #2 Article #9</span>
          <span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-brand-cyan/30"></span>
          <span class="text-brand-sky/60 text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-widest">June 2026</span>
        </div>
        <h1 class="font-heading text-5xl md:text-7xl font-black text-white mb-8 tracking-tight leading-[1.1]">
          Web Designers Near Me vs <br />
          <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-brand-cyan to-brand-blue">Big Agencies: The Local Choice</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-brand-sky/80 leading-relaxed max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          When business owners in Shelby, NC type "web designers near me" they're usually looking for fast, reliable, and affordable solutions. Here's why local expertise wins every time.
        </p>
      </header>

      <!-- Main Image Placeholder -->
      <div class="aspect-video bg-brand-dark border border-white/5 rounded-3xl mb-16 overflow-hidden shadow-2xl relative group">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-blue/20 to-transparent opacity-50 group-hover:opacity-70 transition-opacity"></div>
        <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center">
           <span class="text-brand-sky/20 font-heading text-4xl font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] transform -rotate-12">Shelby Web Company Official</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Content -->
      <div class="prose prose-invert prose-lg max-w-none">
        <p class="text-lg text-brand-sky/90 mb-12">
          At <a href="/" class="text-brand-cyan hover:underline decoration-brand-cyan/30 underline-offset-4">Shelby Web Company</a>, we've helped dozens of local companies switch from generic big-agency websites to custom, high-performing ones that actually grow their business.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mt-16 mb-8 flex items-center gap-4">
          <span class="text-brand-accent">01.</span> Why Local Web Design Shelby Wins
        </h2>
        
        <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-16">
          <div class="bg-brand-dark/50 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-white/5 hover:border-brand-blue/20 transition-all">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4">1. Faster Communication</h3>
            <p class="text-brand-sky/70 text-sm leading-relaxed">No more waiting days for replies from a team across the country. With local web designers near me, you get quick feedback and faster launches.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-brand-dark/50 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-white/5 hover:border-brand-blue/20 transition-all">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4">2. Deep Local Understanding</h3>
            <p class="text-brand-sky/70 text-sm leading-relaxed">We know what works in Shelby, Gastonia, and Charlotte. Our web development is tailored to how local customers search and buy.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-brand-dark/50 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-white/5 hover:border-brand-blue/20 transition-all">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4">3. Better Value & Flexibility</h3>
            <p class="text-brand-sky/70 text-sm leading-relaxed">Big agencies come with big retainers. We offer transparent web design Shelby packages with no long-term lock-ins.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-brand-dark/50 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-white/5 hover:border-brand-blue/20 transition-all">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4">4. Combined SEO Expertise</h3>
            <p class="text-brand-sky/70 text-sm leading-relaxed">As a true SEO agency Shelby, we don't just design — we build websites that rank for "web designers near me" queries.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mt-16 mb-8 flex items-center gap-4">
          <span class="text-brand-accent">02.</span> The "Local Advantage" Interview Checklist
        </h2>
        <p class="text-brand-sky/80 mb-8">Before hiring even a local designer, ask these 5 critical questions:</p>
        
        <div class="space-y-4 mb-16">
          {[
            "Do you build with performance (LCP/FID) or just templates?",
            "How specifically will you optimize for local 'Map Pack' search?",
            "Is the branding research included or do I provide everything?",
            "Who do I call at 6:30 PM on a Tuesday if the site has an issue?",
            "What is the actual data-driven path from a visitor to a phone call?"
          ].map((q, i) => (
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-4 bg-brand-dark/30 rounded-xl border border-white/5">
              <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-brand-cyan/20 text-brand-cyan flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-bold">{i + 1}</span>
              <p class="text-brand-sky/90 m-0">{q}</p>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>

        <div class="bg-brand-blue/5 border-l-4 border-brand-blue p-8 my-12 rounded-r-2xl">
          <p class="text-white font-medium italic mb-0">"At Shelby Web Company, we have detailed answers for all five of these, ready to share during our first consultation."</p>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mt-16 mb-8">What a Professional Website Should Deliver in 2026</h2>
        <ul class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4 list-none p-0 mb-16">
          <li class="bg-brand-dark/50 p-4 rounded-xl border border-white/5 flex items-center gap-3">
            <span class="text-brand-accent">✦</span> <span class="text-brand-sky/80">Lightning-fast loading speeds</span>
          </li>
          <li class="bg-brand-dark/50 p-4 rounded-xl border border-white/5 flex items-center gap-3">
            <span class="text-brand-accent">✦</span> <span class="text-brand-sky/80">Mobile-first design</span>
          </li>
          <li class="bg-brand-dark/50 p-4 rounded-xl border border-white/5 flex items-center gap-3">
            <span class="text-brand-accent">✦</span> <span class="text-brand-sky/80">Built-in lead capture tools</span>
          </li>
          <li class="bg-brand-dark/50 p-4 rounded-xl border border-white/5 flex items-center gap-3">
            <span class="text-brand-accent">✦</span> <span class="text-brand-sky/80">Strong local SEO foundation</span>
          </li>
          <li class="bg-brand-dark/50 p-4 rounded-xl border border-white/5 flex items-center gap-3">
            <span class="text-brand-accent">✦</span> <span class="text-brand-sky/80">Modern, trustworthy branding</span>
          </li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mt-16 mb-8">Real Local Success Stories</h2>
        <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-24">
          <div class="bg-brand-dark/50 p-8 rounded-3xl border border-white/5 italic">
            <p class="text-brand-sky/80 mb-4">"Shelby Web Company really knocked it out of the park. Our online presence is generating so many leads now!"</p>
            <p class="text-white font-bold not-italic">— Ryan "Kris" Jones</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-brand-dark/50 p-8 rounded-3xl border border-white/5 italic">
            <p class="text-brand-sky/80 mb-4">"They uncovered opportunities we wouldn't have known otherwise. Our website is generating business beautifully!"</p>
            <p class="text-white font-bold not-italic">— Paul Richardson</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- CTA Section -->
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-blue to-brand-dark p-12 rounded-[2rem] text-center relative overflow-hidden">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_50%_50%,rgba(132,204,22,0.1),transparent_70%)]"></div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-black text-white mb-6 relative z-10">Stop Overpaying for Average Results.</h2>
          <p class="text-xl text-white/80 mb-10 relative z-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
            Ready for web design Shelby that truly understands your business and your community?
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center relative z-10">
            <a href="/contact" class="cta-glow-shine bg-brand-accent text-[#0A0A0A] px-10 py-4 rounded-xl font-bold text-lg hover:bg-brand-accent-light">
              Get Started Today
            </a>
            <a href="tel:7044738188" class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-md text-white border border-white/20 px-10 py-4 rounded-xl font-bold text-lg hover:bg-white/20 transition-all flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z"/></svg>
              (704) 473-8188
            </a>
          </div>
          <p class="text-white/40 text-sm mt-8 relative z-10">
            Special Offer: Free professional logo design + $100 referral bonus.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Footer navigation -->
      <footer class="mt-24 pt-12 border-t border-white/5 flex flex-wrap gap-8 items-center justify-between">
        <a href="/blog" class="text-brand-sky/60 hover:text-white transition-colors flex items-center gap-2">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7"/></svg>
          Back to Blog
        </a>
        <div class="flex gap-6">
          <a href="/" class="text-brand-sky/60 hover:text-white transition-colors">Home</a>
          <a href="/services/web-design" class="text-brand-sky/60 hover:text-white transition-colors">Web Design</a>
          <a href="/contact" class="text-brand-sky/60 hover:text-white transition-colors">Contact</a>
        </div>
      </footer>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
